    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver with an honest, used overall presentation. It shows the kind of cosmetic wear, blemishes, and aging you would expect from a vehicle that has been driven and not kept as a collector-quality example, but it should still be a reasonable option for someone looking for a usable car at a more approachable price point. Expect visible paint and trim wear, an interior with some age and use, and the possibility of minor deferred items or upkeep typical of an older driver. This is not a perfect car, but for the right buyer it could be a solid budget-friendly option that presents decently and can be enjoyed as-is while improving over time.",
      "price": 16900.0,
