    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for the right buyer who wants a project, parts car, or something to sort out over time. This one is clearly in poor condition and shows significant wear, so it\u2019s best suited for someone realistic about the work it needs. That said, it could still make sense for a handy owner or enthusiast looking for an affordable entry point.",
