    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical option for a buyer seeking affordable transportation, a starter project, or a dependable spare. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values value over cosmetics, but it still offers a straightforward ownership opportunity at a highly accessible price. If you want inexpensive wheels with room to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
