      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap, honest runaround that won\u2019t break the bank? This car is a great option for someone who needs affordable transportation and doesn\u2019t mind a vehicle with a bit of character. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s a dependable budget-friendly choice with plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want straightforward value at a sensible price, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Honest driver with solid enthusiast potential. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still offers a strong mechanical foundation for someone wanting an affordable project, commuter, or platform to sort and enjoy. The powertrain starts, runs, and moves out with the kind of straightforward, serviceable character that makes these worth saving, and the chassis still has usable road manners. Expect cosmetic flaws, wear, and deferred items consistent with a budget-priced used vehicle, but for the right buyer this is a chance to get into a capable car without spending big money upfront. If you want a flashy showroom piece, this isn\u2019t it\u2014if you want something you can tinker with, improve, and put to work, this one makes sense.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, well-traveled character you notice right away\u2014a practical ride with plenty of life left for someone who wants dependable wheels with personality. It\u2019s the kind of vehicle that feels right at home as a daily commuter, a first car, or a handy backup to keep around for errands and weekend runs. Not flashy, just straightforward and useful, with a presence that suggests stories already lived and many more still ahead. If you appreciate value, simplicity, and the chance to make a solid, budget-friendly car your own, this one is easy to like.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
